label: شرح زيج سنجق دار. زيج. زيج سنجق دار
Sharḥ Zīj Sanjaq Dār. Zīj. Zīj Sanjaq Dār ... [etc.].
description: Title supplied by cataloger, from the three first texts.

Physical description: 23 lines per page. Written in medium small Maghribī script in black ink with use of red. The text is framed within two black lines. Light cream European paper, glossy. Contains tables, charts , and diagrams. Kabīkaj (reading: "Kīkataj") on first fol. Modern foliation in pencil using Western numerals (omits first fol.).
Origin: The copy of two texts in the volume is dated, beginning of [Dhū al-]Ḥijjah 1200 [Dec. 1786] (fol. 25a) and Thursday, the night of 10 Jumādá al-Awwal 1203 [Feb. 6, 1789] (fol. 29b).

metadata.label: Abstract
value: Collection of short treatises and excerpts on astronomy.

metadata.label: Contents
value: 1. fol. 1b-21b: [Sharḥ Zīj Sanjaq Dār] / Aḥmad ibn Māmī al-Ḥanafī. -- Mach, R. Yahuda, no. 5032.
3. fol. 25b-101a: Zīj Sanjaq Dār / Muḥammad al-Sharīf Sanjaq Dār. -- Mach, R. Yahuda, no. 5031.
4. fol. 101b-118b: al-Sirr al-maktūm fī aḥkām al-nujūm [Excerpts] / Fakhr al-Dīn al-Rāzī.
5. fol. fol. 119a-130a: Urjūzat Abī Ḥusayn ibn ʻAbd al-Raḥmān ... al-Ṣūfī fī al-kawākib al-thābitah fī al-ṣuwar / Abū ʻAlī ibn Abi al-Ḥusayn al-Ṣūfī. -- Mach, R. Yahuda, no. 4873.
6. fol. 130a-149b: Faṣl fī maʻrifat al-ṭāliʻ min al-kawākib ... [etc].
